FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774211656
OL,3,CWhistleblower 'progress' but still
OL,4,Croom for 'improving culture'- NI Audit
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FThe Comptroller and Auditor General
OL,8,FDorinnia Carville's report on Raising
OL,9,FConcerns in the Northern Ireland
OL,10,FPublic Sector follows a number of high-
OL,11,Fprofile cases associated with raising
OL,12,Fconcerns in recent years.
OL,14,FThe report released on Friday notes
OL,15,Fthat more than 700 concerns have been
OL,16,Fraised across the public sector in the
OL,17,Flast five years.
OL,19,FThe largest category of classified
OL,20,Fconcerns relates to potential fraud or
OL,21,Fmaladministration.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774211656
OL,3,CWhistleblower 'progress' but still
OL,4,Croom for 'improving culture'- NI Audit
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FIn cases where investigations were
OL,8,Fcompleted, only 10% of the concerns
OL,9,Fraised were upheld.
OL,11,FAll government departments now have
OL,12,Fupdated policies and a designated
OL,13,Fofficer in place to deal with
OL,14,Fwhistleblowing, which was seen as
OL,15,Fpositive.
OL,17,FHowever, areas for improvement were
OL,18,Falso identified, including the need
OL,19,Ffor development of specialised,
OL,20,Finvestigative skills, to ensure that
OL,21,Fall concerns are appropriately treated.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774211656
OL,3,CWhistleblower 'progress' but still
OL,4,Croom for 'improving culture'- NI Audit
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FThe report also calls for more sharing
OL,8,Fof good practice and reflection on
OL,9,Fwhat works between organisations, and
OL,10,Fstronger leadership across public
OL,11,Fsector organisations on raising
OL,12,Fconcerns.
OL,14,FThe report highlights that in many
OL,15,Fgovernment departments 'speak up
OL,16,Fchampions' are not in place, despite
OL,17,Fthis being a requirement of the 2023
OL,18,Fframework.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774211656
OL,3,CWhistleblower 'progress' but still
OL,4,Croom for 'improving culture'- NI Audit
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FCommenting on the report's findings,
OL,8,FMs Carville said a "healthy and
OL,9,Fpositive culture around raising
OL,10,Fconcerns is essential to ensure
OL,11,Ftransparency, integrity and
OL,12,Faccountability within the public
OL,13,Fsector".
OL,15,F"It helps organisations detect issues
OL,16,Fearly, avoid costly mistakes, and
OL,17,Fimprove service delivery for the
OL,18,Fpublic," she said.
OL,26,@pD@TOUuD@GO]wD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774211656
OL,3,CWhistleblower 'progress' but still
OL,4,Croom for 'improving culture'- NI Audit
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,F"The 2023 NI Departments' Raising a
OL,8,FConcern Policy Framework was a very
OL,9,Fsignificant and welcome step forward.
OL,11,F"However, public sector leaders should
OL,12,Fcontinue to treat this as a priority
OL,13,Fand ensure their staff are informed,
OL,14,Fskilled and supported to raise
OL,15,Fconcerns they have as well as manage
OL,16,Fthose they receive.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774211656
OL,3,CWhistleblower 'progress' but still
OL,4,Croom for 'improving culture'- NI Audit
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,F"Alongside this report today, I am
OL,8,Fdelighted to publish an updated Good
OL,9,FPractice Guide on Raising Concerns to
OL,10,Fsupport public sector bodies and their
OL,11,Femployees.
OL,13,F"This guide, together with the
OL,14,Frecommendations in my report, will
OL,15,Fhelp central and local government
OL,16,Fassess their current arrangements and
OL,17,Fcreate the environment where raising
OL,18,Fconcerns is encouraged, welcomed and
OL,19,Fmanaged effectively."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
